        <!-- About Us Section -->
        <div class="about-us px-5 py-5 mx-auto">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <h2>OUR PURPOSE</h2>
                        <hr />
                        <p>
                            The Chhattisgarh Photography Dealer Welfare Association is a non-profit organisation. CPDWA
                            wants to get all unorganised regional photographers and videographers associations under one
                            roof to represent in Government for securing benefits to its affiliated members.
                            <br><br>
                            We believe that photography is not just a hobby or a profession, but an art form that has
                            the power to capture and preserve memories and moments in time.
                            <br><br>
                            Our mission is to support, uplift and develop the photography industry in India by providing
                            our members with a wide range of resources and opportunities for growth and education. We
                            strive to create a community where photographers of all levels can come together to share
                            their knowledge, skills, and passion for photography.
                            <br><br>
                            We offer membership to anyone who is interested in photography, whether you are a
                            professional photographer, an amateur photographer, or just someone who loves taking
                            pictures. Our membership includes access to educational workshops, networking events, and
                            other resources that will help you to improve your skills and advance your career.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-center" data-aos="fade-down">
